C08030&quot;&gt;sloom0 &amp;gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;yyyeah I hate escape strings dont know how they work at all&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;out &amp;gt;&amp;gt; @&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;send you a DM :| question about the broken audpip&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#302010&quot;&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;mclark &amp;gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;slime was a late theme now&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#302010&quot;&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;mclark&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt; ha&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#6688AA&quot;&gt;https://wikitext.info/sp/NbG0MD24pPflcUBCImage.png&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;@sloom0&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;#i pipelines and themes... we used to just edit .htaccess in vim and run make... Now you need a whole cloud infrastructure just to change a color... whatever...&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
